</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_228" id="113r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_228_r1l23">Der Stat cʒu Jngelſtat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_228_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als wir euch vormals etwieofft <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l25"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>man</expan> keppfen . hanſen Metmans vnd vlrıch harpentels <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l26"><expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wegen </del> vnd irs leipgdings wegen das ſie von euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l27"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>dyſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l28">fürbraht / vvie daʒ Jr Jn daſſelb Jr leipgding noch niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l30">
<del rend="strikethrough"> be </del> gericht 
<del rend="strikethrough">oder </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134412120_2126">vnd </ab></add> becʒalt 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſey </del> habt / vnd Jn das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒieht</expan> / anders </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l32"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> Jr brief auſʒvveiſen die ſie darümb von euch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des ſie 
<add>vaſt</add></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l34">
<add><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134434158_2146">cʒeſchade </ab><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134438325_2151">kumen </ab></add> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . daſſelb Jr leipgding noch on </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l36">lenger vercʒigen richten vnd becʒalen vnd ſie darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l37">vnklaghaft <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet Als etc Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l38"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan> Jnuocauit </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_228" id="113r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Ingelstat</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir euch vormals etwieofft
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Keppfen, Hansen Metmans
            und Ulrich Harpentels, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, und irs leipgdings wegen, das sie von euch
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                <expan>dyselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber fürbraht, wie daz ir in dasselb ir leipgding noch
            niht gericht <add>und</add> beczalt habt und in das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czieht</expan>,
            anders <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ir brief auszweisen, die sie darümb von euch
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, des sie <add>vast</add>
<add>cze schade kumen</add>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> dasselb ir leipgding noch on lenger verczigen richten und
            beczalen und sie darümb unklaghaft <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan> invocavit.</ab>
</div>
